Package taskallocation

Interface ITaskExecutor

All Known Implementing Classes:
WordCounter
public interface ITaskExecutor
Interface for the execution to be done by the worker once task is allocated to it by the master.

  • Method Details

    • execute

      void execute​(Task task)
      Implementations must add custom execution logic for the obtained task. The implementation must input from the file given in Task and must output to the file given in the same task.
      Parameters:
      task - Task to be accomplished.

      Specific log message for task executor component.
      Parameters:
      message - Specific message.
      application - Name of the application executing the executor.
